6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Mangools and RankMath share a solid foundation of core features including Keyword Research, Rank Tracking, Serp Analysis. Where Mangools pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Backlink Analysis and Competitor Analysis, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, RankMath uniquely offers Content Optimization and Ai Writing and Reporting, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Mangools holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while RankMath scores 8/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, RankMath comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Mangools begins at $49/mo. RankMath stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Mangools requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
